Various Artists - The Stuff That Dreams Are Made Of [2006] [Compilation]

THE STUFF THAT DREAMS ARE MADE OF: SUPER RARITIES & UNISSUED GEMS OF THE 1920s & '30s
A double CD packaged in a DVD digipak; 46 country and blues gems, including many never heard before! Two previously unknown Son House sides, a newly discovered Georgia Pot Lickers, a completely unknown track from Louis Jordan, Tommy Johnson, Dock Boggs, Memphis Jug Band, Sweet Brothers, Andrew and Jim Baxter, and many others -- cover art by uber-collector Robert Crumb! Yow!
